  "description": "Minendra Rijal is a prominent Nepali politician known for his association with the Nepali Congress party. He has held several significant ministerial positions, including Defence Minister, Minister of Information and Communications, and Minister for Constituent Assembly, Parliamentary Affairs and Culture. He has been elected to the House of Representatives from Morang-2 and was a member of the Constituent Assembly. Regarded as a scholarly figure in Nepali politics, Rijal was a key architect of the country's mixed electoral system. He holds a PhD in Management from New York University, where he also lectured for three years.",
